snippet.title: From Nava Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Escape the lab in Late 2024!

Wishlist the game today!
store.steampowered.com/app/2721750/From_Nava/

In From Nava, you are equipped with only a seemingly ordinary pen, but it possesses the extraordinary ability to unleash magic attacks by drawing specific patterns. You must escape from this abandoned research laboratory by gathering all the keys and polaroids left behind in the aftermath of an unknown incident. Various monsters and puzzles are all that stand in your way from fulfilling a stranger's final wish and unravel the mysteries of the world and yourself.
